<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="9Feb1932"><font color="red">9 February 1932</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to T.S. Eliot): Mr Joyce &hellip;owner of world rights &hellip; <i>Ulysses</i> &hellip; 4 conditions: 1) There will not be any preface; 2) The text is to be published unabridged and unaltered; 3) The publication is to be made as soon as possible; 4) The text of the 11th Paris edition is to be read by an expert proof reader. </div>
